ing your customers? Even if they do create a small biz video, they might not know how to rank it for keywords. That is where great guides like this one come in to help succeed online.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_11_0) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36','',0,0),(8,32,'dorinvatamanu18@gmail.com','dorinvatamanu18@gmail.com','','172.22.0.1','2017-05-22 10:18:50','2017-05-22 10:18:50','Great article Brian. On a somewhat related tangent, when embedding YouTube videos into pages I have found it can hurt the loadspeed of the pages. Obviously this is poor for SEO. What are your thoughts on this? I have taken to using a plugin that embeds a still from the video with the play button on it as an image. If the user clicks it then loads the YouTube video. It has done wonders for loadspeed.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_11_0) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36','',0,2),(9,32,'dorinvatamanu18@gmail.com','dorinvatamanu18@gmail.com','','172.22.0.1','2017-05-22 10:39:52','2017-05-22 10:39:52','adsfasdfa',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_11_0) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36','',4,2),(10,34,'David','david@mail.com','http://www.david.com','172.22.0.1','2017-05-23 15:20:11','2017-05-23 15:20:11','Great Article!',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_11_0) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36','',0,0);
